Interface ILevel

All Known Implementing Classes:
ComputerRoomController, FridgeController, LaboDoorController, LaboratoryController, LivingRoomController, SuperLevel
public interface ILevel
This Interface describes the methods of a Main Level-Scene. It is not displayed as a popup, but as a whole 1280x720px scene.
